div.p:
Finallie, that thou mayeſt die both peaceablie and well: In the midſt of the agonie of death,Pſal. 51.5 ſay with that Princelie Prophet DAVID, Into thine hands O LORD 1 commend my Spirit:
                  Luke 23 46 and with our Saviour IESUS CHRIST, Father in thine hands 1 commend my Spirit;
                  Act. 7.59 and with STEVEN, LORD IESVS receaue my Spirit. If at that tyme Sathan, or thine owne conſcience trouble thee, in reſpect of thy guiltieneſſe of ſinnes, and of GODS juſtice, cloſe thine eares at theſe cryes in the agony of death, and anſwere nothing, but commend thy cauſe vnto GOD: Cloſe lykewayes thine eyes in the houre of death, and CHRIST ſhall ſend his Angels to convoy thy ſoule.
